AVG TuneUp
Date First Available ‏ : ‎ August 23, 2019
Manufacturer ‏ : ‎ AVG
ASIN ‏ : ‎ B07WFQV8FK

DISK CLEANER: Deep scans your devices from top to bottom to remove gigabytes of junk files.
BROWSER CLEANER: Removes leftover browsing traces and tracking cookies from 25+ browsers, including Edge, Chrome, Firefox, and IE.
AUTOMATIC SOFTWARE UPDATER: Scans for & fixes some of the most common device problems.
SOFTWARE CLEANUP: Detects & removes 3rd-party trials, ads, and unwanted toolbars.
